what is access modifiers
access modifiers specialized where a property/method is accessible
there are 4 types of access modifiers
1 public
2 private
3 protected
4 default

private access modifiers
private access modifiers access only using methods
here implements data hiding terminology(abstraction)
for access the private access modifiers we need to construct getter and setters

getters and setters syntax
class class_name{
datatype attribute_name1
datatype attribute_name2
.........................
datatype attribute_name n

now create setter and getter
public datatype set_attribute_name(){
 //attribute
}
public datatype get_attribute_name(){
 //attribute
}
}

NB: setter never return any things
NB: only getters return attribute properties/values


